ciscoNetworkVirtualizationOverlayMIB.name: ciscoNetworkVirtualizationOverlayMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoNetworkVirtualizationOverlayMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-snmp@cisco.com
ciscoNetworkVirtualizationOverlayMIB.description: This MIB module is for managing Network Virtualization Overlay functionality on Cisco devices. The following terms are used throughout this MIB: NVE Network Virtualization Endpoint NVGRE Network Virtualization using Generic Routing Encapsulation NVO Network Virtualization Overlay VLAN Virtual Local Area Network VNet Virtual Network VNI Virtual Network Identifier VXLAN Virtual Extensible LAN

cnvoNvoTable.name: cnvoNvoTable
cnvoNvoTable.description: This table provides network virtualization overlays configured on the system.

cnvoNvoEntry.name: cnvoNvoEntry
cnvoNvoEntry.description: An entry containing management information for network virtualization overlay.

cnvoNvoInstanceId.name: cnvoNvoInstanceId
cnvoNvoInstanceId.description: A unique number to identify a NVO instance.

cnvoNvoEncapType.name: cnvoNvoEncapType
cnvoNvoEncapType.description: This object specifies the encapsulation type for the NVO instance. 'unknown' - The read-only value 'unknown' indicates that encapsulation type is none of the following 'vxlan' - encapsulation type is VXLAN 'nvgre' - encapsulation type is NVGRE This object may be modified when the row is active.

cnvoNvoSourceInterface.name: cnvoNvoSourceInterface
cnvoNvoSourceInterface.description: This object specifies the Source Interface for the NVO instance. This object may be modified when the row is active.

cnvoNvoConfiguredVni.name: cnvoNvoConfiguredVni
cnvoNvoConfiguredVni.description: This object indicates the list of VNIs associated with this NVO instance.

cnvoNvoStorageType.name: cnvoNvoStorageType
cnvoNvoStorageType.description: This object specifies the storage type for this conceptual row.

cnvoNvoRowStatus.name: cnvoNvoRowStatus
cnvoNvoRowStatus.description: This object specifies the status of this conceptual row.

cnvoVNetTable.name: cnvoVNetTable
cnvoVNetTable.description: This table provides information for virtual networks on the system.

cnvoVNetEntry.name: cnvoVNetEntry
cnvoVNetEntry.description: An entry containing status information for a virtual network.

cnvoVNetLocalVNetId.name: cnvoVNetLocalVNetId
cnvoVNetLocalVNetId.description: A unique number to identify a local virtual network.

cnvoVNetIpMcastAddrType.name: cnvoVNetIpMcastAddrType
cnvoVNetIpMcastAddrType.description: This object indicates the type of Internet address to be used as Multicast Group Address.

cnvoVNetIpMcastAddr.name: cnvoVNetIpMcastAddr
cnvoVNetIpMcastAddr.description: This object specifies the Internet address to be used as Multicast Group Address. The type of this address is determined by cnvoVNetIpMcastAddrType.

cnvoVNetVlan.name: cnvoVNetVlan
cnvoVNetVlan.description: This object specifies the mapping vlan for the virtual network.

cnvoVNetArpSuppression.name: cnvoVNetArpSuppression
cnvoVNetArpSuppression.description: This object specifies if ARP seppression is turned ON/OFF for the virtual network.

cnvoVNetReplication.name: cnvoVNetReplication
cnvoVNetReplication.description: This object specifies the replication mode of the virtual network identifier.

cnvoVNetHostReachability.name: cnvoVNetHostReachability
cnvoVNetHostReachability.description: This object specifies if the virtual network identifier is configured via data plane, control plane or is unconfigured.

cnvoVNetVniType.name: cnvoVNetVniType
cnvoVNetVniType.description: This object specifies the type of the virtual network identifier - unknown, L2 or L3.

cnvoVNetIpVrfOrBridgeDomainName.name: cnvoVNetIpVrfOrBridgeDomainName
cnvoVNetIpVrfOrBridgeDomainName.description: This object specifies the ip vrf (for L3 vni) or bridge-domain name (for L2 vni) virtual network identifier

cnvoVNetRouterMacAddr.name: cnvoVNetRouterMacAddr
cnvoVNetRouterMacAddr.description: This object indicates the hardware MAC of the physical router.

cnvoPeerTable.name: cnvoPeerTable
cnvoPeerTable.description: This table provides information of remote peers for virtual network overlay on this system.

cnvoPeerEntry.name: cnvoPeerEntry
cnvoPeerEntry.description: An entry containing remote peer information for virtual network overlay.

cnvoPeerIpAddrType.name: cnvoPeerIpAddrType
cnvoPeerIpAddrType.description: This object indicates the type of Internet address of NVO peer.

cnvoPeerIpAddr.name: cnvoPeerIpAddr
cnvoPeerIpAddr.description: This object indicates the Internet address of NVO peer. The type of this address is determined by cnvoPeerIpAddrType.

cnvoPeerUpTime.name: cnvoPeerUpTime
cnvoPeerUpTime.description: This object indicates the time at which the peer became up. This object contains value 0x0000010100000000 when the NVO peer is down.

cnvoPeerLearningSourceType.name: cnvoPeerLearningSourceType
cnvoPeerLearningSourceType.description: This object indicates the way in which in peer was learnt - either via data plane or control plane.

cnvoVNetStatsTable.name: cnvoVNetStatsTable
cnvoVNetStatsTable.description: This table provides statistics information of virtual networks on the system.

cnvoVNetStatsEntry.name: cnvoVNetStatsEntry
cnvoVNetStatsEntry.description: An entry containing statistics information for a virtual network.

cnvoVNetOutUnicastPackets.name: cnvoVNetOutUnicastPackets
cnvoVNetOutUnicastPackets.description: This object indicates the total number of unicast packets transmitted out of this virtual network.

cnvoVNetOutUnicastBytes.name: cnvoVNetOutUnicastBytes
cnvoVNetOutUnicastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for unicast packet transmitted out of this virtual network.

cnvoVNetOutMulticastPackets.name: cnvoVNetOutMulticastPackets
cnvoVNetOutMulticastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of multicast packets transmitted out of this virtual network.

cnvoVNetOutMulticastBytes.name: cnvoVNetOutMulticastBytes
cnvoVNetOutMulticastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for multicast packet transmitted of this virtual network.

cnvoVNetInUnicastPackets.name: cnvoVNetInUnicastPackets
cnvoVNetInUnicastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of unicast packets received by this virtual network.

cnvoVNetInUnicastBytes.name: cnvoVNetInUnicastBytes
cnvoVNetInUnicastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for unicast packet received by this virtual network.

cnvoVNetInMulticastPackets.name: cnvoVNetInMulticastPackets
cnvoVNetInMulticastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of multicast packets received by this virtual network.

cnvoVNetInMulticastBytes.name: cnvoVNetInMulticastBytes
cnvoVNetInMulticastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for multicast packet received by this virtual network.

cnvoNvoPeerStatsTable.name: cnvoNvoPeerStatsTable
cnvoNvoPeerStatsTable.description: This table provides remote peers statistics information for virtual network overlay.

cnvoNvoPeerStatsEntry.name: cnvoNvoPeerStatsEntry
cnvoNvoPeerStatsEntry.description: An entry containing statistics information for a particular peer of a virtual network overlay.

cnvoNvoPeerOutUnicastPackets.name: cnvoNvoPeerOutUnicastPackets
cnvoNvoPeerOutUnicastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of unicast packets transmitted to the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerOutUnicastBytes.name: cnvoNvoPeerOutUnicastBytes
cnvoNvoPeerOutUnicastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for unicast packet transmitted to the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerOutMulticastPackets.name: cnvoNvoPeerOutMulticastPackets
cnvoNvoPeerOutMulticastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of multicast packets transmitted to the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerOutMulticastBytes.name: cnvoNvoPeerOutMulticastBytes
cnvoNvoPeerOutMulticastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for multicast packet transmitted to the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerInUnicastPackets.name: cnvoNvoPeerInUnicastPackets
cnvoNvoPeerInUnicastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of unicast packets received from the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerInUnicastBytes.name: cnvoNvoPeerInUnicastBytes
cnvoNvoPeerInUnicastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for unicast packet received from the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerInMulticastPackets.name: cnvoNvoPeerInMulticastPackets
cnvoNvoPeerInMulticastPackets.description: This object indicates the number of multicast packets received from the peer.

cnvoNvoPeerInMulticastBytes.name: cnvoNvoPeerInMulticastBytes
cnvoNvoPeerInMulticastBytes.description: This object indicates the number of bytes for multicast packet received from the peer.

cnvoMIBCompliance.name: cnvoMIBCompliance
cnvoMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for CISCO-NETWORK-VIRTUALIZATION- OVERLAY-MIB.

cnvoNvoGroup.name: cnvoNvoGroup
cnvoNvoGroup.description: A collection of objects providing NVO information.

cnvoVirtualNetworkGroup.name: cnvoVirtualNetworkGroup
cnvoVirtualNetworkGroup.description: A collection of objects providing VNI status information.

cnvoPeerGroup.name: cnvoPeerGroup
cnvoPeerGroup.description: A collection of objects providing NVO peer information.

cnvoVirtualNetworkStatsGroup.name: cnvoVirtualNetworkStatsGroup
cnvoVirtualNetworkStatsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing virtual network statistics information.

cnvoNvoPerPeerOutUnicastStatsGroup.name: cnvoNvoPerPeerOutUnicastStatsGroup
cnvoNvoPerPeerOutUnicastStatsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing transmitted peer unicast statistics information.

cnvoNvoPerPeerInUnicastStatsGroup.name: cnvoNvoPerPeerInUnicastStatsGroup
cnvoNvoPerPeerInUnicastStatsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing received peer unicast statistics information.

cnvoNvoPerPeerInMulticastStatsGroup.name: cnvoNvoPerPeerInMulticastStatsGroup
cnvoNvoPerPeerInMulticastStatsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing received peer multicast statistics information.

cnvoNvoPerPeerOutMulticastStatsGroup.name: cnvoNvoPerPeerOutMulticastStatsGroup
cnvoNvoPerPeerOutMulticastStatsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing transmitted peer unicast statistics information.
